sed without my approval. If you wish to quote from them at all I shall consider this only after you have submitted to me a copy (taped). I am rather puzzled by finding here and there in the chitchat phrases and terms neither my wife nor I ever use. (All the farcical germanic "Akhhs...!!!" with which you introduce the speeches of your Russian characters must go, of course.)





Vladimir Nabokov





TO: PROF. STEPHEN JAN PARKER1

TL (XEROX), 1 p.





Montreux-Palace Hotel

